# The Inverted Stack — environment overrides
#
# Copy this file to `.env` at the repo root and fill in real values. The .env
# file is gitignored. The Makefile (`build/Makefile`) loads it via `-include`
# and `export`, so values land in the environment of any tool the Makefile
# invokes (audiobook.py, imagegen.py, voice-pass.py, etc).
#
# Format: simple KEY=value lines, no quotes, no spaces around the equals sign.
# Comments and blank lines are fine.

# --- TTS / audiobook ------------------------------------------------------

# Bearer token for the Windows Chatterbox/higgs TTS server. Required when
# --engine chatterbox is selected (make audiobook-chatterbox,
# audiobook-sample-chatterbox, audiobook-voices-chatterbox).
TTS_API_KEY=

# Chatterbox server URL. Default is the Tailscale hostname; override to LAN
# IP when off-network.
# CHATTERBOX_URL=http://desktop-umt08rn:8881/v1

# Dropbox base for audiobook deploy. Defaults to
# ~/Library/CloudStorage/Dropbox.
# DROPBOX_AUDIOBOOK_BASE=

# --- Galley (writing-tool integration) ------------------------------------

# Override where galley-managed build artifacts (audio, alignments) land.
# GALLEY_BUILD_ROOT=
# GALLEY_BOOK_ID=the-inverted-stack
# GALLEY_AUDIO_DIR=
# GALLEY_ALIGNMENT_DIR=
